      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite and regression history; ISO 9001-compliant QMS records available.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1) is under version control with a documented regression test suite covering 47 benchmark cases. QMS records satisfy ISO 9001 requirements. Achieved level meets required level 3 for MRL 5."
    },
    {
