      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests confirm solver convergence rate matches theoretical expectations for transport equations relevant to hemolysis prediction.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to the Navier-Stokes and scalar transport equations confirms second-order spatial accuracy. Code verification is complete and documented in the solver validation report."
    },
    {
