      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments replicate COU geometry, fluid, operating range, and boundary conditions; no major extrapolation flags identified.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the identical FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry at the same five flow-speed combinations defined in the COU. Bovine blood properties match the intended clinical fluid analogue. No extrapolation beyond the validated operating envelope is required."
    },
    {
