      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Boundary conditions applied in the simulation are shown to be equivalent to those measured experimentally within stated uncertainty bounds.",
      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profiles derived from PIV measurements are applied as CFD boundary conditions. Rotational speed matches tachometer readings within 0.2%. Fluid temperature and viscosity equivalency confirmed by rheometry. Input parameter equivalency is established across all operating points."
